# AeroCraft Project Structure

## Library (src/)
```
src/
  types/
    config.types.ts      — AeroCraftConfig, AeroCraftResolvedConfig
    shortcuts.types.ts   — ShortcutDefinition, ShortcutGroup
    index.ts
  constants/
    numbers.const.ts     — all magic numbers
    defaults.const.ts    — DEFAULT_PREFIX, DEFAULT_MODE, etc.
    groups.const.ts      — GROUP_ORDER, GROUP_LABELS
    shortcuts.const.ts   — ALL_SHORTCUTS, FLEX_SHORTCUTS, etc.
    index.ts
  core/
    parser.ts            — resolveConfig, buildClassName
    generator.ts         — generateCSS, generateStandaloneCSS
  postcss/
    plugin.ts            — aerocraftPlugin (PostCSS plugin)
    index.ts
  index.ts               — public API, defineConfig
```

## Shortcut Definition Pattern
Every shortcut has:
- `name` — kebab-case shortcut name (without prefix)
- `group` — one of GROUP_ORDER values
- `utilityRecipe` — optional multi-class recipe string for docs and tooling
- `css` — equivalent standalone CSS properties
- `description` — one-line plain English description

## Adding a New Group
1. Add group name to GROUP_ORDER in groups.const.ts
2. Add GROUP_LABELS entry
3. Add group toggle to AeroCraftGroupsConfig in config.types.ts
4. Add DEFAULT_GROUPS entry
5. Create shortcut definitions in shortcuts.const.ts
6. Add group to ALL_SHORTCUTS
